## A note on how this book is made

This is a folder of linked HTML files generated from Markdown by a small Python build.
The table of contents lives in one file (`toc.py`); the prose lives in `content/`.
A chapter that is not written yet renders as a navigable stub from its planned outline, so the whole book is always browsable.
See `CLAUDE.md` for the authoring workflow.

Nothing here is final.
It is a scaffold meant to be argued with, corrected, and filled in.
